column5: LET THE PICTURES DO THE TALKING sorry about the quality..... cell          YOU KNOW YOU WAAAAANNT IT !!!!!!!!!  BE THERE OR BE SQUARE!!!!!!!!  BITEME Looking for a 2fer
Nobody ever said anything about a trophy!!  Nice!  Tony
Ahhh yess.....  completely plated in pure artificial 24 carat gold, smelling of minnows and stale ole' milwaukee...  A trophy any real angler would be proud to have his/her name on!
I understand Jumla's are banned from the tourney this year.....
I say we all chip in and buy Lew a Lakair muskie this year.... lol...  (sorry bud...)
Here's a nice Lakair musky from last September TJ, but if you can buy me a bigger one in 3 weeks, well then, I'll gladly accept !!
looks like a musky to me
Where do i sign up?  FOTB
THERE IS  A TROPHY??  Looks at schedule , wonders if she can rearrange...  Daydreams...  But a trophy , wow!  Jen
Nice ski Lew.     I hope you do get a bigger one in 3 weeks.  I also hope to make it up next year, to meet some OFC members and catch a few fish.  FOTB
You should definetely plan on joining us next year FOTB, it's guaranteed to be one of your best trips of the year !!
Look out boys, that trophy needs a gals name on it - Mine -  This is my year, I can feel it  Joey
WAY GOOD TIME!!!!!!!
You stand an excellent chance to win this year Joey , you just need to stick the hooks in the fish this time, rather than yerself
Good Point Lew, I'll try to keep that in mind  Joey

HaaHaa, Now that was a good one.

thats an awfully big word you got their douG but can you spellit too???   Art

Je ne sais quoi?... isn't that a women depillatory?   Yer right there Joe... 'cept about 4 states further South!!!   You got that sheeeeee-it right!!!
Think again BiteMe,the only reason you won was..to busy helping somebody else in a time of need.The names on that trophy say it all.May the next to win stand up.  Steve
